sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant GW as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Engine Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/TLS
    participant Router as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>(Init Container)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 1: InferenceService (RawDeployment + Istio Mode)

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (optional)
    IstioGW->>Predictor: Forward via VirtualService<br/>HTTP/80, Istio mTLS
    Note over Predictor, S3: Model loading (init container, at pod startup)
    StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, AWS/GCP/Azure credentials
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    Predictor-->>IstioGW: Prediction response
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService (Gateway API + GIE)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    GW->>Scheduler: Route via InferencePool<br/>HTTP/8080 or gRPC, Istio mTLS
    Scheduler->>vLLM: Route to optimal engine<br/>HTTP/8000, TLS (self-signed)
    Note over vLLM, S3: Model loading (init container, at pod startup)
    StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Cloud credentials
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    vLLM-->>Scheduler: Completion response
    Scheduler-->>GW: Response
    GW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Pipeline

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /v1/models/{graph}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS (edge)
    IstioGW->>Router: Route to graph router<br/>HTTP/8080
    Router->>Predictor: Step 1: Pre-processing model<br/>HTTP/80, Istio mTLS, Bearer propagated
    Predictor-->>Router: Step 1 result
    Router->>Predictor: Step 2: Inference model<br/>HTTP/80, Istio mTLS, Bearer propagated
    Predictor-->>Router: Step 2 result
    Router-->>IstioGW: Combined pipeline result
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443
